text:
Rushia-daitenshi is more unstoppable this time... :_るんるん:
And with that Minecraft Update...
And the adventure was in Netherworld (Dante's inferno or Hades) for obtaining too rare minerals and interchanging gold to "warriors" for obtain goodies like... Some rare materials...
Sorry sorry... I don't play Minecraft with the few things I can see... Well... :_きゅん:

We were with the heart pumping due to Yabainess of making a bridge over magma and trying to not to fall...

Also stream had the good BGM selection, starting with Ucchii0-sama's "Be Happy" :_サイリウム碧: :_サイリウム紫:

And Supaachaato Orei Time had "Summer Triangle" mainly.
Noticed about these Rainbow Naisupas... :_ちょうちょ: Totally ideal to end the 2020 and start 2021.

Nice for Rushia at second form. :_ハート:
